    'wr_subject' => 'Busan Polytechnic-KME signs MOU to add work-study parallel system',
    'wr_content' => '<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">(CNB = Reporter Choi Won-seok) The Busan Campus of Korea Polytechnic University (President Do Jae-yoon) is looking for answers at the corporate site for the early settlement of the parallel work-study system.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">To this end, the Busan Campus visited KME Co., Ltd. (CEO Sung Jae-yeon) on the 15th and announced that it signed an MOU to promote an organic mutual cooperation system and a work-learning parallel system.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">KME is a manufacturer of ship lighting equipment and electrical equipment, and it is participating in Daewoo Shipbuilding &amp; Marine Engineering System in particular in recognition of its expertise in the field of withstand voltage explosion-proof switches. It also discussed discussions on joint research project development through this agreement, which will also participate in Kazakhstan\'s state-run project.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Sung Jae-yeon, CEO of the company, said, "We plan to hire technical part-in-one this year. I want to raise high school graduates from the bottom of the recruitment process so that they can get a degree."</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dean Do Jae-yoon said, "If we participate in the degree-linked contract department (electricity department) of the work-study parallel system, it will be a good opportunity to obtain a degree along with improving job skills because learning workers receive full tuition and work and learn at the same time. The contract department will organize an education curriculum focused on field work and reflect the opinions of companies as much as possible.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Through this work-study parallel system, we intend to contribute to the development of the local economy by jointly growing local companies and our universities."</span>',
